---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me | Kristy Wong - VFX Artist">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12">VFX Artist & Digital Creator</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
        <!-- Profile Image -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Replace with your actual profile image -->
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gray-700 relative flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500">
              <span class="text-lg">Profile Image</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Skills Section -->
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Skills</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">3D Animation</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">95%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 95%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Visual Effects</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">90%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 90%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Compositing</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">85%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 85%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Motion Graphics</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">80%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 80%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Rigging</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">75%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 75%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- About Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <h2>My Story</h2>
            <p>
              Hi, I'm Kristy Wong, a passionate VFX artist with expertise in creating stunning visual effects and animations. With over [X] years of experience in the industry, I've had the privilege of working on a variety of exciting projects across film, television, and digital media.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              My journey began with a fascination for blending art and technology to create immersive visual experiences. I graduated from [Your University/School] with a degree in [Your Degree], which provided me with a strong foundation in both technical skills and creative storytelling.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-8">Experience</h2>
            <p>
              Throughout my career, I've collaborated with talented teams on projects ranging from blockbuster films to innovative digital campaigns. My expertise includes [list your specific expertise areas like particle simulations, fluid dynamics, character animation, etc.].
            </p>
            
            <p>
              I've worked with leading studios such as [Studio Name] and [Studio Name], contributing to projects like [Project Name] and [Project Name]. These experiences have honed my ability to deliver high-quality visual effects that enhance storytelling and create memorable viewer experiences.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="mt-8">My Approach</h2>
            <p>
              I believe that great visual effects should seamlessly integrate with the narrative, enhancing the story without overpowering it. My approach combines technical precision with artistic vision, always striving to push the boundaries of what's possible while maintaining a focus on the emotional impact of the work.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              When I'm not creating visual effects, I enjoy [mention hobbies or interests that might be relevant], which continuously inspire my creative process and bring fresh perspectives to my work.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-8">
              <h2>Software & Tools</h2>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Maya</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Houdini</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Nuke</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">After Effects</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Cinema 4D</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">ZBrush</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Substance Designer</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm">Unreal Engine</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition">
              Get In Touch
            </a>
            <a href="/portfolio" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 ml-4 bg-transparent border border-purple-500 hover:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition">
              View My Work
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout> 